title: United Kingdom Imports of Milling Industry Products
description: Imports of Milling Industry Products in the United Kingdom increased to 41.42 GBP Million in September from 38.67 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Milling Industry Products in the United Kingdom averaged 21.22 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 43.82 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 7.63 GBP Million in April of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Milling Industry Products.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
